Sentencas: Rapid thermal-cycling tests were performed for the thick-film, electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Rapid Thermal-Cycling Test Using Thick-Film Electrolyte-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The sintered yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film was mounted on a YSZ ring by sintering the two pieces together.
Titulo: Rapid Thermal-Cycling Test Using Thick-Film Electrolyte-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: With this configuration, it was possible to cycle the cells between 200 and 800 degrees C with heating and cooling rates up to 50 degrees C/min.
Titulo: Rapid Thermal-Cycling Test Using Thick-Film Electrolyte-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Using La(0.6)Sr(0.4)Co(0.2)Fe(0.8)O(3-delta) as a cathode and Ni-GDC (Gd-doped ceria) as a composite anode, the cell with a 50 mu m thick YSZ electrolyte maintained a high performance, i.e., maximum power density of similar to 510 mW/cm(2) at 800 degrees C after thermal cycles.
Titulo: Rapid Thermal-Cycling Test Using Thick-Film Electrolyte-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: A planar SOFC was highly durable for rapid thermal cycles.
Titulo: Rapid Thermal-Cycling Test Using Thick-Film Electrolyte-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
